아 그리고 이 무대에서 '내일은 꼭 두 주먹을 꽉 쥐고' 여기서 석민이랑 승관이 목소리 둘다 뚜렷하게 들려서 너무 좋아함

author: @heyitsmira17
text:
I always... ALWAYS cry when watching any Pretty U performance, for some reason. It all starts cute and fun, but around the "I can't take it no more", my heart becomes a bit heavy, then during DK and Seungkwan's lines it just gets harder and harder, but what triggers my tears is the "Seventeen, saranghae, yeppeuda!" fanchant. I just cried for 5 minutes bc of Pretty U again, I _really_ can't take it no more orz. 

Maybe it's because it was my first era and their first win, or bc the song is so beautiful and full of feelings idk I am just crying alone at home while filled with the same joy I had 3 years ago. Seventeen, thank you for everything you've given me as a carat. I really love you guys. Have a happy chuseok ♡ and maybe someday please consider coming to Brazil ;-----;
